 When I saw the timetable issued by American Airlines in 1967, I found an interesting thing 

00:00:18.950 --> 00:00:25.660
 From the timetable, the flight time from New York to Los Angeles is 5 hours and 43 minutes 

00:00:25.660 --> 00:00:26.660
 But this may not be the case 

